                      ### Requirements

                      * Support nested scopes
                      * Aggregate over time
                      * Rank top memory-heavy scopes

                      ### Example Output

                      ```
                      Top memory-heavy scopes (last 60s):
                        - process_batch: +120MB
                          - deserialize: +80MB
