                          ## 8. Async Support

                          ### Problem

                          Async workloads obscure memory attribution.

                          ### Solution

                          Provide:

                          #### Option A: Attribute macro

                          ```rust
                          #[track_memory]
                          async fn process_batch() { ... }
                          ```

                          #### Option B (Preferred): tracing integration

                          * Attach allocation data to tracing spans
                          * Aggregate per-span memory usage

                          ---

                          ## 9. Runtime Modes

                          ### 9.1 Lightweight Mode (Default)

                          * No backtrace
                          * Minimal overhead
                          * Safe for production

                          ### 9.2 Debug Mode

                          * Enable backtrace tracking
                          * Detailed diagnostics
                          * Higher overhead

                          ### Enforcement

                          * Backtrace must be feature-gated
                          * No heavy operations in allocation hot path

                          ---

                          ## 10. Configuration Improvements

                          ### 10.1 Environment-Based Config

                          Support:

                          ```
                          HEAP_SENTRY_MODE=debug
                          HEAP_SENTRY_INTERVAL=1000
                          HEAP_SENTRY_GROWTH_THRESHOLD=1048576
                          ```

                          ---

                          ### 10.2 Zero-Config Initialization

                          ```rust
                          heap_sentry::init();
                          ```

                          ---

                          ### 10.3 Feature Flags

                          * `tracing`
                          * `prometheus`
                          * `backtrace`

                          ---

                          ## 11. Performance Guarantees

                          ### Requirements

                          * Lock-free hot path (atomics only)
                          * No allocations inside allocator hooks
                          * Background thread handles heavy work

                          ---

